    "auditedTables": [
      "builds",
      "agents",
      "constitutional_checks"
    ],
    "reasoning": "Audit timestamps are essential for tracking builds and their statuses. CUIDs are chosen for unique and sortable identifiers. No soft deletes are needed since the focus is on read-only access, and cascade deletes are avoided to maintain data integrity."
